com.kaazing.net.auth

Class NegotiableChallengeHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kaazing.net.auth.ChallengeHandler
      • com.kaazing.net.auth.NegotiableChallengeHandler

  • public abstract class NegotiableChallengeHandler
extends ChallengeHandler
    A NegotiableChallengeHandler can be used to directly respond to "Negotiate" challenges, and in addition, can be used indirectly in conjunction with a NegotiateChallengeHandler to assist in the construction of a challenge response using object identifiers.
    See Also:
    RFC 4178 Section 4.2.1 for details about how the supported object identifiers contribute towards the initial context token in the challenge response.
